As WHEELIE spoke, there was a collective roar from the TERRORCONS as
their humor turned to anger and then even rage!

"I do not smell like snot!" BLOT yelled out.

RIPPERSNAPPER turned over to him, "Actually you do!" He smiled wickedly.

Then there was another roar as GRIMLOCK stepped foward followed by his
DINOBOTS. "Me Grimlock say Wheelie needs our help! Dinobots attack
Terrorcons!"

"NO!!" Yelled BACKSTOP who's voice somehow managed to rise above the
noise. The volume caused the others to pause for a moment.

BACKSTOP looked from the DINOBOTS to the TERRORCONS. "No." He said
more quietly this time. "We have a bigger target then ourselves."

"And just what's is that?" HUN-GRR said in derisive tones.

Pulling out a small device BACKSTOP looked again to the TERRORCONS and
DINOBOTS, "Our true foe is Magmatron!"

Pressing a button on the device a portal opened, and through it the
sounds of a battle could be heard.

(TAG)

- Preston
